                  <li>• Minimum 1 sq ft per 300 sq ft of attic space</li>
                  <li>• 50% intake (soffit) / 50% exhaust (ridge) ratio</li>
                  <li>• Continuous ventilation preferred over spot vents</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Ventilation Benefits</h3>
                <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
                  <li>• Prevents ice dam formation in winter</li>
                  <li>• Reduces cooling costs in summer</li>
                  <li>• Prevents moisture buildup and mold growth</li>
                  <li>• Extends roof shingle lifespan by 20-30%</li>
                  <li>• Maintains consistent attic temperatures</li>
